<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-PK">
<head>
  <!-- Same meta tags as index.html -->
  <title>Privacy Policy – GharFix Pakistan</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar from index.html -->
  <main id="main">
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Last updated: <span id="lastUpdated"></span></p>
        
        <div class="card glass mt-4">
          <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
          <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, book a service, or contact support.</p>
          
          <h3 class="mt-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
          <p>We use your information to provide, maintain, and improve our services, process transactions, and communicate with you.</p>
          
          <h3 class="mt-3">3. Data Security</h3>
          <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information.</p>
          
          <h3 class="mt-3">4. Contact Us</h3>
          <p>Questions about this policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:smarttoolsuniverse2026@gmail.com">smarttoolsuniverse2026@gmail.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <!-- Footer from index.html -->
  <script>
    document.getElementById('lastUpdated').textContent = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-PK');
  </script>
</body>
</html>
